title: Hogan
overview: The young Hogan, with supernatural abilities, gets involved in the killing of Suleiman in defense of Bahloul, then gets involved in stealing a villa with Lotfi, Horus and Noga, but Kamal Al-Labbad takes advantage of Hogan's power by making him his personal guard, while Warda continues her search for him and approaches him in order to marry him.
